<item>
            <title>[SEC-2017] ActiveDirectoryLdapAuthenticationProvider.doAuthentication() does not catch IncorrectResultSizeException</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SEC-2017</link>
                <project id="10040" key="SEC">Spring Security</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The mentioned method uses Spring LDAP Template to search for the given user in AD. However, if the given user does not exist at all in the directory, the template throws IncorrectResultSizeException and not NamingException, as expected.&lt;/p&gt;

